>Reopen in Dev Container
in container: npm run dev

"Dev Containers: Rebuild Container" after modifyien devcontainer JSON

Dev Containers: Reopen Folder Locally to exit container or click bottom left

test post route:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/users -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"username": "john_doe", "email": "john@example.com"}'

test get route:
curl http://localhost:3000/users/john_doe

Database schema (SQLite):
-- Users table
CREATE TABLE users (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
  username TEXT,
  email TEXT
);

-- Posts table that RELATES to users
CREATE TABLE posts (
  id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
  title TEXT,
  content TEXT,
  user_id INTEGER,
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id)  -- ðŸ‘ˆ RELATIONSHIP!
);

to override env variables:
NODE_ENV=development PORT=3001 npm run dev